text: The 2015 Acht van Westerveld was the 9th running of the women's Acht van Westerveld, a women's bicycle race in the Netherlands starting and finishing in Dwingeloo. It was rated by the UCI as a 1.2 category race. ==Results== ==See also== * 2015 in women's road cycling ==References== ==External links== * Category:Ronde van Drenthe (women's race) Drentse 8 van Dwingeloo Drentse 8 van Dwingeloo
